content.query:
SELECT [Fetch_CHE_Id]
,[Put_CHE_Id]
,[CarryCompleteDate]
,[First_Lift]
,[Last_Lift]
,[Move_Count]
,[WorkTime]
,[Year]
,[Month]
,[Week]
 FROM [dbo].[yard_che_productivity]
 WHERE (Fetch_CHE_Id = 47
 or Put_CHE_Id = 47)
 AND DATEPART("day",CarryCompleteDate) = 1 And Year= 2022 and Month = 10
 order by [CarryCompleteDate]
